text: Eda IF is a sports club in Eda in Sweden. It was established in November 1941 as a ski jumping and soccer club. The women's soccer team was started in 1974. The women's soccer team played in the Swedish top division in 1982. In 2007 the club began to play floorball. ==References== ==Other websites== *Soccer *Floorball Category:1941 establishments in Sweden Category:Floorball clubs in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs Category:Ski clubs in Sweden
